		"description": "<p>Whenever an enemy attacks you, if you have no Judgment Dice, roll your Judgment dice (2d6). On your next melee attack this encounter, if you hit, deal that much additional radiant damage. The dice are expended whether you hit or miss.</p><hr><p>Level 3: Your Judgement Dice are d8s</p><p>Level 5: Your Judgement Dice are d10s</p><p>Level 8: Your Judgement Dice are d12s</p><p>Level 10: Your Judgement Dice are d20s</p><p>Level 14: Whenever you roll Judgement Dice, roll 1 more</p>",
